title: Pivot/Bh Demo
description:
BH/Pivot and Canyon Bicycles of Millcreek Bicycle demo event.
Cyclists are welcome to demo both BH road and Pivot mountain bikes.
course: Participants will meet at Rotary Glenn Park 800 South 2770 East. Mountain riders will ride shore line north the Red Butte Canyon and back. Road riders will ride up Emigration Canyon and back. Both rides will take approximately 45 minutes to an hour.
registration:
Registration the day of only at Rotary Glenn Park. 
Every participant must sign release form and wear a helmet.

title: USU Mountain Bike Race
description: This is a cross country race at Sherwood hills on a 5 mile loop and a short track race at Renegade Sports on their motocross track.
course:
The cross country loop is a 5 mile loop that is mostly flat with small rolling hills. 

The Short track is a motocross course at a Renegade Sports. It has rhythm sections, woops, berms, and some tables. The loop is about 1 mile long.
registration: Day off registration only. One race is $20. Register for both races on the first day and its only $30.00.
notes:
Renegade Sports Short Track- Registration at 4pm. 
Men C 5:15pm, Women B at 5:45pm, Men B at 6:15pm, Women A at 6:50pm, and Men A at 7:30pm. 

Sherwood Hills XC - Registration at 8am. 
Mens C, Womens B, and Womens A start at 9am. 
Mens B and Mens A start at 11am.

Questions contact ericgardiner@gmail.com
directions:
To Renegade Sports from South- Head north on highway 89 from Brigham city. It is just after the Flying J and has the largest flag in Logan. Address is 1903 S 800 W Logan Utah. 

To Sherwood Hills Resort from South - Head north on highway 89 from Brigham city. It is 11 miles north of Brigham City on the west side of the road.
